sentences: This issue (FCCC/KP/CMP/2012/8) was first taken up by the SBI plenary on 27 November.
SBI Chair Chruszczow consulted with interested parties.

Final Outcome: In its conclusions (FCCC/SBI/2012/L.30), the SBI takes note of the annual report of the administrator of the international transaction log under the Kyoto Protocol, and agrees to continue its consideration of its recommendations at SBI 38.
